placing footwear on the user's foot and thereby locating the sensor between the user's foot and the footwear;
collecting data relating to sensed conditions while the user wears the footwear;
augmenting collected data with user information; and
providing user-specific recommendations for footwear that fits the anatomy of the user's foot.

